{"tid":1334561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣上訴結果","createTime":"2019-07-20T07:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:38:07.000Z","uid":253573,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99d941880c143b507a29eaa798ddbf2ef1310214","tid":1334561,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:00:01.000Z","msg":"1435 【上訴結果】<br />\n<br />\n上訴委員會就民陣上訴作以下裁決：<br />\n－民陣需呼籲參與市民「立即解散」；<br />\n－結束時間由晚上9時改為晚上11時59分；及<br />\n－終點維持於灣仔盧押道。<br />\n<br />\n民陣將嚴格按不反對通知書安排遊行。警方在上訴期間，指遊行人士在到達終點後，可往皇后大道方向，即向南行解散，而不反對通知書中要求民陣安排遊行人士「立即散去」，因此，民陣只能盡力呼籲大家「立即散去」，唯按不反對通知書，民陣沒有責任，亦沒有能力在相關區域安排離開灣仔的交通方法，因此明日散去的交通方法，還請各位當日向安排能力「傑出」、「智力過人」的警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n民陣重申，民陣將盡最大努力，保障遊行路線上參與人士的安全。而任何混亂，還請警方負上全責。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQhgj8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQhgj8X.jpg&h=968ddd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民陣需呼籲參與市民「立即解散」 唔好再屌佢地趕人走 <br />\n聽日見!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f52e320d138b49aa3b62f9550b87019c5960ae3e","tid":1334561,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721 721"},{"pid":"5ba7443a66dc9163f28a4c6eda7a56f9e9df339c","tid":1334561,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acfbd4651dc26220b75fb254da1e29b68a16be2","tid":1334561,"uid":89974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"其實夜晚9點仲好，到時和理非飯都未食就清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民反警<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n鬥爭可避則避，但如避無可避一定要郁手，係cam面前讀咗呢段先盡量保護自己：<br />\n如打人：<br />\n你襲擊39，現在行使公民拘捕權！(最好比佢實質打中先用，否則未必入到)<br />\n<br />\n如有傷害：<br />\n你傷人19，現在行使公民拘補權！<br />\n<br />\n如有黑社會自爆：<br />\n你聲稱三合會成員，現在行使公民拘補權！<br />\n<br />\n如有冒警人士兼有帶攻擊性武器(記住一定要有埋武器先可以，否則唔夠level用)：<br />\n你非法管有攻擊性武器，現在行使公民拘補權！"},{"pid":"80825e1551ff1163bb2d25cc66aa3e23c8040e65","tid":1334561,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:27:31.000Z","msg":"721 721"},{"pid":"56498db8d4aa5e81fd5b1c9dc8e00d4da2b52da2","tid":1334561,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891019c4dd387e0f54ed5d2806c8316d400ce515","tid":1334561,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db07e189eceeab0842be176bb3d5abd8b4eb0c8b","tid":1334561,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ff50aa2b84c695c23580bfeea0c7f2fbc15dfe","tid":1334561,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike"